ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectNational Film Board - Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving that the National Film Board enter into a collective agreement with the PROFESSIONAL INSTITUTE OF THE PUBLIC SERVICE OF CANADA that covers all employees in the Technical Category,the Administrative Support Category and the Operational Category for the period beginning on July 1,2022 and ending on June 30, 2026.
